column16: Jay Bruce flies out to center fielder Eddie Rosario.
Todd Frazier called out on strikes.
Joey Votto singles on a line drive to left fielder Eduardo Escobar.   Eugenio Suarez scores.    Billy Hamilton scores.    Ivan De Jesus to 2nd.
Mike Leake out on a sacrifice bunt, pitcher Alex Meyer to second baseman Brian Dozier.   Eugenio Suarez to 3rd.
Scooter Gennett homers (4) on a fly ball to right center field.
Aramis Ramirez homers (9) on a line drive to left field.   Carlos Gomez scores.
Carlos Gomez singles on a soft fly ball to right fielder Torii Hunter.   Ryan Braun scores.
Adam Lind grounds out, first baseman Joe Mauer to pitcher Alex Meyer.   Ryan Braun to 3rd.
Jonathan Lucroy flies out to right fielder Torii Hunter.
Gerardo Parra flies out to right fielder Torii Hunter.   Scooter Gennett to 3rd.
